<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>VoteChain : Online Voting Platform</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="mainContainer">
      <%- include('component/header') %>

      <div class="mainContent">
        <div class="leftContent">
          <img src="/assest/img/index_illu.png" class="img-fluid-w" alt="" />
        </div>

        <div class="rightContent">
          <p class="tagLine">Easy, Secure and Fast Voting Platform</p>
          <p class="description">
            VoteChain is a fast, easy, and secure online voting platform powered
            by blockchain technology. It ensures transparency, prevents fraud,
            and guarantees tamper-proof results. With a user-friendly interface,
            VoteChain makes elections seamless for organizations, communities,
            and businesses. Experience trustable digital voting with end-to-end
            encryption and decentralized security.
          </p>

          <a href="/user/auth" class="primary-btn">Login/Register</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="keyFeatureContainerOuter">
        <div class="blockTitle">Key Features</div>

        <div class="keyFeatureContainer">
          <div class="featureCard">
            <div class="featureImage">
              <img src="/assest/img/easy-feature.png" class="img-fluid-w" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="featureContent">
              <p class="featureTitle">Easy to Use</p>
              <div class="featureDescription">
                A user-friendly interface makes voting effortless for everyone. No technical knowledge requiredâ€”just log in, vote, and confirm your choice in seconds.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="featureCard">
            <div class="featureImage">
              <img src="/assest/img/fast-feature.png" class="img-fluid-w" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="featureContent">
              <p class="featureTitle">Fast Response</p>
              <div class="featureDescription">
                Blockchain technology ensures instant vote recording and verification, eliminating delays. Real-time results make elections seamless and efficient.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="featureCard">
            <div class="featureImage">
              <img src="/assest/img/secure-feature.png" class="img-fluid-w" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="featureContent">
              <p class="featureTitle">Secure Voting</p>
              <div class="featureDescription">
                Every vote is encrypted and stored on an immutable blockchain ledger, preventing fraud, tampering, and unauthorized access for ultimate election integrity.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
